------------------------------------------------------------
-- Open Questions
------------------------------------------------------------

open question "For X/G calibration, which comb-slot subset is required before calibration may be applied: every slot, fixed head/foot reference slots, or a sampled set per comb?"
open question "Should winding expose pause/resume at every macro boundary, every continuous-wrap step, or only at explicit recipe breakpoints?"
